@startuml
title Architecture (vue simple)
skinparam shadowing false
left to right direction

rectangle "Client\nNavigateur web" as client
rectangle "Front-end\nReact (SPA)" as fe
rectangle "Back-end\nAPI Symfony (REST)" as be
database "Base de données\nMySQL" as db
cloud "Service externe\nText-to-Speech" as tts

client --> fe : Utilisation
fe --> be : Appels HTTP\n(JSON)
be --> db : Données (CRUD)
be --> tts : Synthèse vocale

note bottom of be
Logique métier + sécurité
(rôles USER / ADMIN)
end note

@enduml

